title: TFW Your entire team is toxic.

replies.body: Thats what I get every time I Ahri ADC, but they are suprisingly chill with Udyr mid.

Play Singed top and your jungler flames, Warwick support and nobody bats an eye...
######It's happened to me

I mean with warwick support, you can execute minions with Q to heal you both a sizable amount, your ult basically locks down a guy, and you can see low health enemies nearby. Not to mention you can give attack speed.
